item.title: About Me
item.description: My name is Rohan Rajan. I am a senior pursuing Computer Science at NIT Trichy. I am currently interested in issues surrounding the advancement of ethical data practices and machine learning. I enjoy breaking systems and trying to build from the bottom up. Check out my resume here
